            <lg xml:id="TK1163">
<l>kāmamu nāṇu muyirkāvāt tūṅkumeṉ </l>
<l>ṉōṉā vuṭampi ṉakattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(Both) lust and shame, with my soul for their shoulder pole balance themselves on a body that cannot bear them.</l>
